## Page Templates

### API Reference Page
```markdown
# [Method] [Resource]  
`[HTTP_METHOD] /v1/endpoint`

[One sentence: what this endpoint does and when to use it.]

## Parameters

| Field | Type | Required | Description |
|-------|------|----------|-------------|
| ...   | ...  | ...      | ...         |

## Returns

[What the response object is. Link to the object reference.]

## Example request

[Code tabs: curl, Node.js, Python, Go]

## Example response

[Full JSON response body]

## Errors

| Code | Description | Resolution |
|------|-------------|------------|
| ...  | ...         | ...        |

## Related
- [Link 1]
- [Link 2]
```

### Conceptual Guide Page
```markdown
# How to [accomplish goal]

[One sentence: what this guide covers and what you'll have at the end.]

## What is [core concept]?

[2-4 sentence plain English explanation. Analogy if helpful.]

## Before you begin

- [Prerequisite 1]
- [Prerequisite 2]

## Step 1: [Imperative verb phrase]

[1-2 sentences of context]

[Code example]

[What you should see / verify]

## Step 2: [Imperative verb phrase]

...

## Testing

[How to test this in sandbox/staging. Include failure scenarios.]

## Next steps

- [Related guide 1]
- [Related guide 2]
- [API reference for objects used]
```

